<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 A public hearing is being held in response to industry requests to amend the Carolina, Tennessee Valley, and Louisville-Lexington-Evansville
Federal milk marketing orders. Several proposals would amend the pooling standards of the Tennessee Valley and Carolina
orders; one proposal would change the marketing areas of the Tennessee Valley and Louisville-Lexington-Evansville
